# Domain invariants (use `docs/DOMAIN_SCHEMAS.md`)

- Money is represented as integers (minor units) and must always include an explicit `currency`.
- Do not use floating-point arithmetic for financial calculations.
- Transactions are immutable; historical data must not be silently overwritten.
- Source is informational only (input source should not change canonical identity/business meaning).
- No financial calculation without currency.
